twitvend.git - yet another useless twitter search (YAUTS)

search twitter for hashtags and people using their search API
written in Sinatra and templating in HAML

How to use: http://pizzavendingmachines.com

Search for hashtag like #sinatra http://pizzavendingmachines.com/sinatra

Search for user like @franksinatra http://pizzavendingmachines.com/@franksinatra


